{"tid":1627193,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係搞唔掂有無人可以幫下小弟","createTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:00:28.000Z","uid":229403,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca42993e007f90803a309a24d8da55d42315f0c","tid":1627193,"uid":229403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"小弟真係走頭無路 所以先開post求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之從6月發夢之後小弟一直都冇返工<br />\n本身同屋企人關係都唔太好 <br />\n佢地淺黃都有屌柒黑警咁<br />\n佢地就一直叫我唔好出去發夢話香港好亂啲警犬係人就拉<br />\n9月頭佢地終於知道左我有出去發夢之後就一直屌尻我 <br />\n依加仲無比生活費我 仲話12月學費要我自己交<br />\n我依加都係靠飯卷勉強生活到<br />\n小弟搵過幾份工但時世唔好全部都話唔要人<br />\n我真係冇撚晒錢 連返學都係跳閘再行路返去<br />\n有無工可以介紹比小弟 但學費我真係唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b307496dd71b87be96754f3bb980139b703853d","tid":1627193,"uid":229403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:56:04.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"662b1635af1a334caf8c3c4469b0607827812821","tid":1627193,"uid":299788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"其實我都幫唔到你，除咗比錢，唯有幫你推。<br />\n<br />\n你那個是大學學費還是什麼？"},{"pid":"052704b6272ed3209ec097e25e53d2b81bc08b8c","tid":1627193,"uid":229403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"9d1fe7db63ebf2d8e1c81ea91e10c1d869ba804c","tid":1627193,"uid":229403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"cb2a064fc087a37512127e4e5321ba7c50172284","tid":1627193,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"2cce1120586d74aaccf99d4e0b341ffa9bdf5604","tid":1627193,"uid":229403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"dc8f081e6ab1cb7f8b15aa89f34740976ba5ac4f","tid":1627193,"uid":229403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime